@startuml
title UC-06 Emergency SOS Dispatch - Activity Diagram

|Customer|
start
:Press SOS Button;

|System|
:Request GPS Location;

|Google Maps API|
:Provide GPS Coordinates;

|System|
:Capture Current Location;

|Customer|
:Select Vehicle;
:Enter Issue Description;

|System|
:Identify Nearby Approved Garages;
:Filter Garages by Coverage and Availability;
:Broadcast Emergency Alert;
:Start 60-Second Acceptance Timer;

while (Garage Accepted?) is (No)

  :Expand Search Radius;
  :Retry Emergency Broadcast;

endwhile (Yes)

:System Assigns Emergency to First Accepted Garage;

|Garage Owner|
:Review Emergency Details;
:Select Available Mechanic;

|Mechanic|
:Receive Assignment Notification;
:Open Navigation;
:Travel to Customer Location;
:Send Live GPS Updates;

|Customer|
:Track Mechanic in Real Time;

|Mechanic|
:Mark Arrival;
:Perform Repair;
:Mark Repair Complete;

|System|
:Update Emergency Status to Completed;

stop

@enduml